     Corporate Foundation Profiles (Sixth Edition) contains

     Corporate Foundation Profiles (Sixth Edition) contains
detailed profiles of 251 of the largest corporate foundations in
the United States, including the foundations' purposes, giving
limitations, names of officers and directors, financial data,
analyses of recent grants, and application guidelines.  Data are
also provided for an additional 600 corporate foundations with
assets of at least $1 million or annual giving of $100,000 or
more.  The book costs $125, plus $2 for postage.  Order it from
The Foundation Center, 79 Fifth Avenue, New York, NY 10003, (800)
620-4230.



