Department's Antitrust Division between December 18, 1995 
and January 16, 1996. 

ANTITRUST DIVISION CONTROL NO.: AT95-369 
DATE: 12/18/95

REQUESTED BY: Ralph O. Barton Jamestown, ND 58402-1900

MATERIAL REQUESTED: Correspondence from or to schools in North Dakota, the
North Dakota School Board Association or the North Dakota Attorney
General's Office discussing an alleged conspiracy "between 1966 and 1988 to
allocate customers and rig bids for school buses and school bus bodies in
North Dakota."

