Order No.:  GAO/IMTEC-91-17BR
Pages:  26

To assist Congress in its continuing oversight
responsibilities, GAO reviewed the Department of Defense's
fiscal year 1991 budget request for information technology
resources.  GAO identified potential reductions of $460.1
