Order No.:  GAO/NSIAD-91-65
Pages:  16

GAO reviewed the Navy's aircraft procurement budget request
for fiscal year 1991 and appropriations for the preceding
two years to identify potential budget reductions and
rescissions, including amounts that are not being used for
the purposes appropriated. GAO identified $972.1 million in
