JANUARY 5, 1996

THE 25 HOTTEST AREAS FOR HMO GROWTH


RANK MARKET

1 Galveston TX

2 Springfield IL

{3 Cedar Rapids IA

{3 Lubbock TX

{3 Ft.  Smith AR

{3 Biloxi MS

7 Merced CA

